Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s already left. It would seem that\Nshe’s determined not to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, I guess you’re still too young\Nto understand a woman’s feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…\NBy the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the rumor that Unit 04 went missing true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that there was some kind\Nof accident, and it exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 04 vanished, along with\Nthe Second Branch of Nerv.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened while they were\Ntesting the S2 engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But don’t worry, we’ll be all right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of our Evas are functioning properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have a crack team of pilots and staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that Unit 03 is being\Nbrought here from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re performing the activation tests\Nat Matsushiro, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll be out for four days or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but Kaji will be taking care of you two,\Nso don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko will be there as well, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There won’t be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, about the pilot…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve come today with a request, Major Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Make me the pilot\Nfor Evangelion Unit 03!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.30,Title Cards3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1274.749,288.5)}{\fs58}EPISODE 18\N{\fs75}SELECTION\NOF LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Shinji doesn’t know yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding the right time to tell him…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I just can’t tell\Nwhat the heck he’s thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re the one who volunteered\Nto be his guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So when are you calling in the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that’ll be tomorrow.\NThere are a lot of things to prep, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He might tell Shinji himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn’t enthused enough\Nto be bragging about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting his sister transferred to\Nour hospital here at Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was the one condition he gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Miss Misato sure can be cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m number one when it comes to enthusiasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so she could at least use me,\Neven if it’s just as a backup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Toji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? You left before me,\Nbut you’re awfully late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What, no marital spat today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn’t want to see your ugly faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You three damn stooges!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where’s Toji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even eating lunch? Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s been acting odd lately, hasn’t he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayanami, if you’re lookin’ for Shinji,\Nhe ain’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You know ’bout me, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems Sohryu knows too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So Shinji’s the only one who doesn’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You don’t usually care ’bout people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I’m not sure I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you care about’s Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s have lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hours late, and then, finally, he arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s the first guy to ever make me\Nwait this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because you never waited for the guy\Nwhen you were dating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this was the so-called Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time I was living in a place\Ncalled Nebukawa,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but the rising water levels caused\Nby the melting of Antarctica
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,have submerged it beneath the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.08,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, transfer student,\Nbut I’ve gotta beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t feel right until I’ve smacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Asuka. You always\Nwalk home with Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. The only reason I’m with Shinji\Nis because of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don’t feel like seeing him today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is about Suzuhara, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You could tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The three stooges are about\Nthe only ones who don’t see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ikari seems naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, he’s the most dense of them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And he’s an idiot to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn’t know how to relate to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Suzuhara might like Miss Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara does?! Miss Perfect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They seemed to be getting along during lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, Hikari. There’s no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She’s a million times denser than Shinji is\Nabout relating to people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you see in that hot-headed stooge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,His kindness…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji sure spends a lot of time in the tub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who’s going to pilot Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you haven’t heard yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you two fighting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two always like this\Nwhen Katsuragi’s gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I get to spend the night with you, after all,\Nso I’d love to be all happy and smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can’t do it tonight. I just can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. Let’s go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to bed early is the best thing\Nfor these situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asleep yet, Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s my father like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you’d ask about Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it seems like you’re\Nalways with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s the Vice Commander who’s always with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been asking around\Nabout your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I haven’t been around him much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don’t really know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I’ve learned a lot about him lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,About his work, about my mother, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re wrong there. You only\Nbelieve that you’ve learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,People can’t understand others completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows if you can even\Nunderstand yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding each other one hundred percent\Nis impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.36,0:09:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that’s why we spend so much time\Ntrying to understand ourselves and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what makes life so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that also true for you and Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The word we use for “she” literally\Nmeans “the woman far away”.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To us, women will always be\Non the distant shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, there’s a river dividing men and\Nwomen, deeper and wider than the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,T minus 300 minutes to Unit 03 activation test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.06,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996.818,688.5)}TEST SITE 2, MATSUHIRO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Main power supply, no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.40,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(986.591,693)}TEMPORARY UNDERGROUND CAGE {\fs50}(UNMANNED)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Second apoptosis is nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:52.61,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(947.727,717.75)}SAME SURFACE FACILITY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Coolant systems are normal in all sectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Repairs to left arm crimp lock completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.61,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964.091,511.417)}EVA UNIT-03 ACTIVATION EXPERIMENT\NINTEGRATED CONTROL POSITION
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Team B, commence operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:09:58.99,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988.636,607.917)\c&HF1E9FF&}ON BOARD CENTRAL GENERAL\NCOMMAND VEHICLE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems detected in\Nthe data link to Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It could even go into combat as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That’s nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that was a half-hearted reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, once this unit is cleared for duty,\Nit’ll be assigned directly under your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The exclusive control of four Evas…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted to, you could destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you told Shinji yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I will when the test is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fourth Child has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Second squad, begin readying\Nthe entry vehicle immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s not here yet, is he, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He may not be coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might finally eat together today…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 03’s already in Japan, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think it got here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice. I wonder who’s going to pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s Toji? He’s absent today, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry plug fixed in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiating first connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmitting pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Graph readout is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.02,0:11:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Checklist cleared up to 1350.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems found in initial contact phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Shift the operation to phase two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All nerve links are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Checklist cleared up to 2550.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All harmonics are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We are now exceeding the absolute border.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Abort the test! Break the circuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No good! High energy readings\Ndetected in body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion has occurred in Matsushiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage level unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the rescue squad and the Third Troop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of it before the SSDF gets involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Movement of an unidentified object\Ndetected at the site.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern is orange. We can’t\Nconfirm it to be an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to battle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel, battle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for ground combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch all Eva units!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch immediately to intercept locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Air transport is scheduled to go in twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An accident in Matsushiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Then, are Miss Misato\Nand the others okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t contact them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you blubbering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Worrying about them right now\Nwon’t get us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But how can we fight the Angel by ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari is taking direct command now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My father is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a visual of the target at Mt. Nobe.\NTransferring to main monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Transmit the abort signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Force eject the entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not working. Neither abort signal\Nnor plug ejection code accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have respiratory and cardiac\Nresponse, but he’s probably…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 03 will be\Nabandoned at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be designated as the Thirteenth Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy the battle line at Mt. Nobe as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All units prepare for ground combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel? Is that an Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct, that is the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that this is the target,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but it’s an Eva, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But that’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it have been taken over by an Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it’s piloted by a human too?\NA child our age?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don’t know?! The pilot of Unit 03 is…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 02 has gone silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot has ejected. Recovery squad\Nis heading for retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is moving towards Unit 00!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei, avoid close range combat\Nand stop the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sending Unit 01 over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Angel is invading Unit 00’s left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The nerve systems are being corrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sever the left arm. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don’t cut the neural connections first…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sever it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 00 is severely damaged.\NThe pilot is wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is approaching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It will contact you in twenty.\NYou must destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But this target is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t there a person in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Another child my own age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.70,0:16:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,An entry plug!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a person in there, just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Problems in life support!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot’s in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good! Cut the synch rate to 60%!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ikari, at this rate, the pilot will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, why don’t you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But there’s a person in there, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant! It is an Angel! Our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But… but I can’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ve got to save them! I can’t just kill somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t care! It’s better than killing someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind! Cut all synchronization\Nbetween the pilot and Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. Switch the control circuit\Nto the dummy plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But the dummy system still has\Na lot of problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and without Dr. Akagi’s approval…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It’ll be of more use than the pilot. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.11,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do, Father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Reception of the signal, confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Control system switch is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All nerves linked directly to the dummy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,32.8% of Emotional Elements are unclear.\NThey can’t be monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Irrelevant. Release the system.\NCommence attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the power of the dummy plug?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,System status nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gain still increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, stop! Stop doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it! Stop it! Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,STOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 03, no, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the target is completely silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll make this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kodama, Nozomi, and I…\NThis recipe is for four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he’ll eat it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ve found a survivor over here too!\NHe’s still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Third squad, erase 807 data\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Send help right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Second squad, please hurry and check\Nfor survivors in the linear block.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You were lucky, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn’t hurt as bad as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Eva Unit 03?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It was apparently destroyed,\Nas an Angel, by Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I… I haven’t told Shinji anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, so you’re all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had something important to tell you, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I begged him to stop, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, I’m sorry. I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Report from the entry plug recovery team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot’s life signs are confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 03’s pilot is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fourth Child is…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Toji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.83,0:21:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:22:00.46,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1539.388,717.333)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.69,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji finally, of his own will,\Nquits as an Eva pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But regardless of his decision, the strongest of\Nthe Angels attacks, giving rise to a new tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: “A Man’s Battle”
